channel.title: Are you into photography ? Check out this thread!
channel.description:
Hey, if you're a photographer freak like me, and would like to see some of my less than amazing shots, see here: http://www.lasercommunity.com/viewtopic.php?t=9198
Wickedlasers.com btw ;) That's here I got the items I took my photos of. ( Lasers, Dragon Case, Goggles, whatever else. ) If you want to make a purchase, and want 5% off of any purchase in your cart, then click this link, and then continue with your shopping :D http://wickedlasers.com/index.php?refer=10678 I highly suggest getting 5% off ;)
Please comment on the photos, either on this forum, or on that one!
Thanks, Swift

Please re-check it =P, you wont be let down.
